channel.title: [508]TokkulScape V1 Source[508]
channel.description:
Welcome to TokkulScape V1. First of all I wanna thank you taking time to read this. This is my First ever Release so please keep the flaming to a minimum. I did use Bulby's Source as a base. I will be releasing a V2 later on, depending on if people like this one or not. In this version there's everything Bulby had and some more. There's personal things such as log ins, staff zones, and so on. Godwars is only 75% in this version, only because I don't know the code for the Zamorak God so I cannot add him just yet. There's Only one quest. Called Dragon Slayer of course.. There's 85% Dueling, that's because when you die in duel arena you lose your stuff. There's pking, and of course, all the skills are 100% trainable. (Not exactly like runescape training skills). There's teleport commands, and teleports by Quest Tab. Okay now onto commands and pictures. Oh yeah, you can use any client you want. I'm just providing a 508 ip switcher client, for those who don't have one. You can also duel anyone any where and any time you want. If they accept of course. Has everything Bulby's source had and more! Oops, just noticed I left some of the character files before I uploaded. So you can delete them yourselfs. Sorry the other client download links canceled, so I'll post em up later!
NOTE: MY YOUTUBE ACCOUNT IS CLOCKWISE27, NONE OTHER!! PEOPLE PRETENDED TO BE ME WHEN THEY WEREN'T!! SUCH AS TOKKULSCAPE508 ON YOUTUBE IS NOT ME..
